>
  <section>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Hi, ich bin Alex. Software Engineer, Webdeveloper und AI Enthusiast. <br
      />
      Co-Founder <a href="https://fino.digital">fino.digital</a> &mdash; M.Sc. in
